{ Counter-attacking on  e4  , a poor move. } 6. Nxe5
{ Grabbing a center pawn. } 6... Qd4
{ Attacking both the pawn and the Knight in the center.   6...Nxe4  loses to  7.Re1  @@StartBracket@@+4.0@@EndBracket@@. }
7. Nf3
{ Saving the Knight, attacking the Queen. White won a pawn @@StartBracket@@+2.5@@EndBracket@@.   7...Qxe4  fails to  8.Re1  @@StartBracket@@+5.5@@EndBracket@@. }
