[Result "*"]

1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 { Ruy López } 3... a6 { Morphy Defense } 4. Bxc6
{ Exchange Variation } 4... dxc6 5. O-O { Normal Variation } 5... f6
{ Gligorić Variation } 6. d4 { Challenging Black's center. } 6... exd4
{ Exchanging a pair of pawns. } 7. Nxd4 Bc5
{ Developing the dark-squared Bishop, attacking the Knight. Black overlooked White's next move... }
8. Qh5+ { Check, forking King and Bishop! } 8... g6 9. Qxc5
