[Result "*"]

1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 { Ruy López } 3... a6 { Morphy Defense } 4. Ba4 Nf6
5. O-O b5 6. Bb3 Bc5 { Neo-Arkhangelsk Variation } 7. Nxe5
{ An interesting temporary piece sacrifice. } 7... Nxe5 8. d4
{ Forking Bishop and Knight in the center. } 8... Bd6
{ Best would have been to take the pawn with the Bishop. After  8...Bxd4  9.Qxd4  , the game is about equal @@StartBracket@@+0.0@@EndBracket@@. }
9. dxe5 { Trading pawns, forking Bishop and Knight again. } 9... Bxe5 10. f4
Bd6 11. e5 { Forking Bishop and Knight for the third time! } 11... Bc5+
{ A zwischenzug, saving the Bishop. } 12. Kh1 Ne4
{ The engine even suggests 12... O-O, that's how bad Black's position is at this point. }
13. Qd5
{ Black's position is collapsing: Checkmate is threatened and the Rook and Knight are under attack @@StartBracket@@+5.5@@EndBracket@@. }
