{ Bird Variation or Bird's Defense. A dubious move: Attacking the Bishop while leaving the pawn on  e5  unprotected. }
4. Nxd4 { Trading a pair of Knights, the best move. } 4... exd4 5. O-O c6 6.
Bc4 d5
