1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nf6 { Petrov Defense } 3. Bc4 { Urusov Gambit } 3... Bc5
{ A very poor move, giving White the initiative. } 4. Nxe5
{ Grabbing a pawn in the center, threatening a fork on  f7  . } 4... O-O
{ Defending  f7  with King and Rook. } 5. d4
{ Chasing away the Bishop, taking control over the center. } 5... Bb6 6. Nxf7
