Nxe4 { Damiano Variation } 4. Qe2
{ Lining up with Black's King while attacking the Knight in the center. } 4...
d6 { Creating a counter-attack, not the best move... } 5. Nxf7
{ A temporarily sacrifice on  f7  , forking Queen and Rook, while still threatening to capture the Knight in the center with check. }
5... Kxf7 6. Qxe4
{ White won an important pawn and Black's King will no longer be allowed to castle @@StartBracket@@+2.0@@EndBracket@@. }
