d5
{ Defending the Knight with a pawn is a mistake!   4...Qe7  is the only playable move in this position. The game could continu with  5.Qxe4  d6  6.d4  dxe5  7.dxe5  Nc6  @@StartBracket@@+1.0@@EndBracket@@.   4...Nf6  loses the Queen to  5.Nc6+  @@StartBracket@@+7.5@@EndBracket@@. }
5. d3 { Attacking the Knight on  e4  . } 5... Nf6
{ This blunder was played hundreds of times... } 6. Nc6+
