9... Qe5 { Threatening checkmate on  h2  while attacking the Bishop on  g5  . }
10. Bxg4 { Removing one of Black's most dangerous pieces. } 10... hxg4
{ Opening up the h-file for the Rook to support a checkmate on  h2  . } 11. g3
{ Preventing checkmate. } 11... Qxg5
{ Grabbing a free Bishop. Black is up a piece for a pawn. All White's pieces are still on the back rank @@StartBracket@@-6.5@@EndBracket@@. }
