{ King's Knight Gambit } 3... d6 { Fischer Defense } 4. d4
{ Conquering the center. } 4... Bg4
{ 4...g5  would have been a better choice. } 5. Bxf4 { Equalizing material. }
5... Bxf3
{ This inferior move was played thousands of times. It isn't the best idea to trade your most active piece in this position! }
