{ Pinning the pawn on  e4  to the King. } 4... Nf6
{ Defending the pawn.   4...Qxd5  is bad in view of  5.Nc3  , forking Queen and pawn on  e4  @@StartBracket@@+2.5@@EndBracket@@. }
