exd4 5. Bg5 { Attacking the Queen. } 5... Qg6
{ Moving the Queen to a safe square.   In case Black played  5...Qd6  , White's best reply is  6.Nxd4  @@StartBracket@@+3.0@@EndBracket@@. }
6. Qxd4
{ Recapturing a pawn in the center. White has developed 4 pieces and is ready to castle next move @@StartBracket@@+4.0@@EndBracket@@. Meanwhile, Black's pieces are having a back rank fest. }
