1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. c3 { Ponziani Opening } 3... Bc5 { A poor move. } 4. d4
{ Taking control of the center. } 4... exd4 5. cxd4 Bb4+ 6. Nc3
{ Blocking the check while developing a piece. } 6... d6
{ 6...d5  7.exd5  Qxd5  @@StartBracket@@+1.0@@EndBracket@@. } 7. d5
