10... Qxd6
{ The most logical reply, keeping the queenside pawn structure intact.   10...d3  is best, e.g. followed by  11.Qd1  Qxd6  12.Be3  @@StartBracket@@+2.0@@EndBracket@@. }
11. Nxd4
