{ Expanding in the center. } 4. exd5 Qxd5
{ Normally you want to capture a center pawn with a Knight, because in normal positions your Queen can be chased away by a Knight. But not in this position: Nc3 is not possible. }
5. Be2
{ A bad move. You need to prevent  e4  , or should leave the  e2  square open for the Queen to pin the e-pawn to Black's King. }
